data.description: This beautiful home is located in the charming and well-established community of Stone Mountain. It has three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, with a grand two-story entryway leading to a formal living and dining room. The house also features a spacious eat-in kitchen and family room, perfect for spending quality time with family and friends. The inviting fireplace and easy backyard access with a comfortable sitting area creates a warm and cozy atmosphere, perfect for relaxing and watching kids play.  The property is conveniently located close to several entertainment and dining options, including the renowned Stone Mountain Park, Wade Walker Family YMCA, and various restaurants. With its ideal location and wonderful features, this house is perfect for creating cherished memories with your loved ones.
